A whimsical Studio Ghibli style illustration of a fantastical bakery factory interior where translucent golden routing slips flutter through the air like magical paper spirits, each slip growing longer and accumulating more handwritten notes as it travels along a winding conveyor belt. In the foreground, a massive mixing bowl overflows with glowing ingredients while tiny spirit creatures carefully attach new paper segments to the flowing documents. The background shows towering storage silos connected by brass pipes and wooden catwalks, with warm afternoon sunlight streaming through tall arched windows, casting long shadows across flour-dusted wooden floors. The color palette features soft creams, warm ambers, and gentle blues, with the routing slips emitting a subtle ethereal glow as they carry the story of each ingredient's journey through the magical production process.
